Edition:
Quote:  Among the various articles to be sent from this Province to the Exhibition at Otago is a splendid collection of Ferns by Mr. R. H. Huntley, Wellington, consisting of five groups in large frames with glass, each forming a distinct landscape picture. They are classified in the following order .. No.3. Nephrolepsis, Polypodium, Pymatodes, Dictymea, Arthropteris, Grammitis, Gymnogramma, Northolaena, Stenchlaena, Lygodium, Schizaea, Leptopteris, and Todea.
