Quote:  Apart from the advantage of attracting tourists it will be found a pleasant resort for families and parties desiring to spend a few days during the summer months where they can procure the pure air to be obtained on the mountain, and see the grand views in some of the gorges where grows the mountain cypress, the lovely crape ferns, (todea superba), the toi, and other plants not to be seen elsewhere.
